These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
City: berlin, paris, venice, hamburg, prague, marseilles, liverpool
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: cricket, ice-hockey, water-polo, handball, climbing, golf, swimming
 1. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
 2. the person who's sport is climbing is the person traveling to hamburg##1
 3. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 4. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
 5. the person traveling to venice is in the middle##1
 6. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far left##1
 7. the person traveling to prague is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 8. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
 9. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
10. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
11. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| City           | prague | hamburg | paris | venice | berlin | marseilles | liverpool |
| Sport   | cricket    | climbing   | handball      | golf | water-polo    | ice-hockey    | swimming         |

