.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: orchid, poppy, azalea, amaryllis, rose, daisy, lily
The people have 7 different hobbies: baking, cooking, card-games, video-games, singing, hiking, board-games
 1. the person who's hobby is singing is the person who growsamaryllis##1
 2. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far right##1
 4. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 5. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 6. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person who growslily##1
 7. the person who's hobby is singing is in the middle##1
 8. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
 9. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
10. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Flower          | orchid | poppy | rose | amaryllis | daisy | lily | azalea |
| Hobby   | cooking      | card-games   | video-games   | singing      | baking       | board-games       | hiking     |

