.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: animation, action, time-travel, romance, disaster, sports, drama
7 different pets are kept: rat, mouse, fish, guinea-pig, hamster, snake, cat
 1. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
 2. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 3. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
 4. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
 5. the owner of the rat is the person watching disaster movies##1
 6. the owner of the fish is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
 7. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
 8. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 9. the person watching sports movies is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
10. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
11. the owner of the guinea-pig is in the middle##1
12. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| Movie-Genre   | action | disaster     | time-travel  | sports       | animation       | drama  | romance   |
| Pet    | snake  | rat | cat | guinea-pig | mouse | fish | hamster |

