.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: volleyball, biathlon, baseball, rowing, parkour, rugby, cricket
There 7 different types of food: peas, onion, eggplant, artichoke, peach, cherry, asparagus
 1. the person who's sport is parkour is the person eating onion##1
 2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 3. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1
 4. the person eating peas is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 5. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 6. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left##1
 7. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 8. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person eating cherry##1
 9. the person who's sport is baseball is the person eating peach##1
10. the person eating peach is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
11. the person eating asparagus is the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
| Sport   | rugby    | cricket     | rowing     | baseball      | biathlon | parkour      | volleyball     |
| Food   | artichoke | eggplant | cherry | peach | asparagus | onion | peas |

