The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: daffodil, tulip, iris, poppy, azalea, amaryllis, dahlia
 1. the dannemann-smoker is the person who growsdahlia##1
 2. the person who growstulip is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
 3. the person who growsamaryllis is in the middle##1
 4. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
 5. the person who growsazalea is the chaman-smoker##1
 6. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
 7. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
 8. the blend-smoker is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
 9. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
10. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| Cigar   | dannemann | blend | chaman     | siglo | vegafina | dunhill | bluemaster |
