.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-6::.
House: cottage, colonial, ranch-style, wooden, craftsman, gothic-revival, cape-cod
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: epic, scientific, romance, comedy, time-travel, superhero, animation
 1. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
 2. the cottage house is the person watching epic movies##1
 3. the craftsman house is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 4. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
 5. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
 6. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the cottage house##1
 7. the wooden house is in the middle##1
 8. the ranch-style house is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 9. the colonial house is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
10. the ranch-style house is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4     |    5    |   6   |      7      |
| House    | ranch-style | gothic-revival   | cottage | wooden | cape-cod  | craftsman | colonial |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy   | time-travel | epic | superhero     | scientific | animation | romance   |

