.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-7::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: fuchsia, ivory, azure, aquamarine, lilac, emerald, red
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: march, december, june, april, july, november, february
 1. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 2. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
 3. the person who likes red is the person who's birthday is in april##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
 5. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in march is the person who likes azure##1
 8. the person who likes lilac is in the middle##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who likes red##1
10. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who likes ivory##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3   |      4       |     5      |     6     |   7   |
| Color   | fuchsia  | red | aquamarine | lilac | emerald     | ivory | azure |
| Birthday     | november | april      | february | june    | july | december   | march  |

