 5. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
 6. the person traveling to berlin is the person playing canasta##1
 7. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person playing go##1
 8. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 9. the person traveling to marseilles is in the middle##1
10. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |       4       |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| City       | london   | san-francisco | miami | marseilles | hamburg     | berlin | prague |
| Game   | chess | domino      | bridge        | snooker         | go | canasta     | mah-jongg |

