.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-20::.
7 different games are played: bridge, scrabble, monopoly, whist, billiard, go, snooker
The people use 7 different means of transport: bus, airplane, subway, boat, jet-ski, skateboard, snowmobile
 1. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left##1
 2. the person playing whist is on the far left##1
 3. the person playing go is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 4. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
 5. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 6. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
 7. the person playing snooker is the person driving the jet-ski##1
 8. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
 9. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
10. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing go##1
11. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3     |     4     |     5     |     6      |   7    |
| Game   | whist | go | snooker  | monopoly | bridge | scrabble | billiard |
| Transport           | skateboard   | airplane    | jet-ski | boat      | subway      | bus | snowmobile   |

 